                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-205-off1078 t18220417-205-cd1079"></join>, one handkerchief, value 4 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220417-205-victim1876" type="victimName">
                           William 
